00:32:42.560 --> 00:32:44.310 align:middle line:10%
Always together
used to practice.

00:32:44.310 --> 00:32:45.990 align:middle line:10%
She never objected.

00:32:45.990 --> 00:32:49.250 align:middle line:10%
Early mornings is to get up
at 4:00 to do the practice.

00:32:49.250 --> 00:32:50.640 align:middle line:10%
She never objected.

00:32:50.640 --> 00:32:52.350 align:middle line:10%
She would help.

00:32:52.350 --> 00:32:58.110 align:middle line:84%
>> After marry, my progress
on yoga is on account of her.

00:32:58.110 --> 00:33:00.760 align:middle line:90%
I use her as a mirror.

00:33:00.760 --> 00:33:04.030 align:middle line:10%
>> They had a really good
understanding of each other.

00:33:04.030 --> 00:33:07.140 align:middle line:10%
He respected my mother
as a householder,

00:33:07.140 --> 00:33:10.140 align:middle line:10%
looking after everything--
looking after the house,

00:33:10.140 --> 00:33:11.900 align:middle line:10%
children, kitchen, everything.

00:33:11.900 --> 00:33:13.920 align:middle line:10%
>> He used to take
her for shopping.

00:33:13.920 --> 00:33:18.270 align:middle line:10%
You see, every Sunday, my
father used to come from Bombay.

00:33:18.270 --> 00:33:22.170 align:middle line:10%
And he used to
reach Pune by 3:30.

00:33:22.170 --> 00:33:26.070 align:middle line:10%
By 4:35, my father used to
take my mother for shopping.

00:33:26.070 --> 00:33:30.390 align:middle line:10%
>> Many times Sunday, he used
to go to Dadar and bring betel

00:33:30.390 --> 00:33:34.350 align:middle line:10%
leaves, because my
mother used to like it.

00:33:34.350 --> 00:33:38.100 align:middle line:10%
On Sunday night, we used
to go for for the walking.

00:33:38.100 --> 00:33:42.150 align:middle line:10%
And my mother, by walking, she
used to make veeda for him.

00:33:42.150 --> 00:33:44.400 align:middle line:10%
And they used to have--
on the road, also,

00:33:44.400 --> 00:33:47.340 align:middle line:10%
so she used to have on
one finger, [INAUDIBLE]

00:33:47.340 --> 00:33:49.680 align:middle line:10%
and another finger leaves.

00:33:49.680 --> 00:33:52.290 align:middle line:10%
We used to wash everything--
clean it, everything.

00:33:52.290 --> 00:33:55.350 align:middle line:10%
And while going,
they used to eat it.

00:33:55.350 --> 00:33:57.350 align:middle line:10%
>> Never they fought
with each other.

00:33:57.350 --> 00:34:00.010 align:middle line:10%
Never there was a quarrel
or fight, in front of us,

00:34:00.010 --> 00:34:01.700 align:middle line:10%
especially.

00:34:01.700 --> 00:34:03.290 align:middle line:10%
It never happened.

00:34:03.290 --> 00:34:07.200 align:middle line:10%
It at all, they had spoken
to each other so differently.

00:34:07.200 --> 00:34:09.300 align:middle line:10%
But there are not
quarrel, as such.

00:34:09.300 --> 00:34:10.860 align:middle line:10%
No argument, as such.

00:34:10.860 --> 00:34:14.550 align:middle line:84%
>> She was really wonderful
lady-- very tolerant lady,

00:34:14.550 --> 00:34:16.350 align:middle line:90%
very helpful lady.

00:34:16.350 --> 00:34:19.830 align:middle line:84%
And looking after everyone
with kind heartedness.

00:34:19.830 --> 00:34:22.600 align:middle line:84%
Both of us lived very
happily for 30 years.

00:34:22.600 --> 00:34:24.860 align:middle line:10%
>> But after passing
of my mother,

00:34:24.860 --> 00:34:27.570 align:middle line:10%
he was both mother and father.

00:34:27.570 --> 00:34:30.420 align:middle line:10%
>> He use to play with
us, especially myself.

00:34:30.420 --> 00:34:36.320 align:middle line:10%
I'm being the eldest daughter
of Guruji, of my father.

00:34:36.320 --> 00:34:38.400 align:middle line:10%
I think I enjoyed a lot.

00:34:38.400 --> 00:34:43.859 align:middle line:10%
>> We used to play on his body
when he used to do practices

00:34:43.859 --> 00:34:47.010 align:middle line:10%
in different asanas,
like Halasana.

00:34:47.010 --> 00:34:48.900 align:middle line:10%
We use to play slide.

00:34:48.900 --> 00:34:52.690 align:middle line:10%
When he used to
do Yoganidrasana,

00:34:52.690 --> 00:34:55.770 align:middle line:10%
we used to play like
see-saw on his body.

00:34:55.770 --> 00:35:00.570 align:middle line:10%
>> You won't believe it, even at
this-- as a three years child,

00:35:00.570 --> 00:35:07.250 align:middle line:10%
I was always doing in front of
him something like toppling.

00:35:07.250 --> 00:35:09.510 align:middle line:10%
Sometimes, I'd touch my toes.

00:35:09.510 --> 00:35:11.970 align:middle line:10%
When he jumped, I will jump.

00:35:11.970 --> 00:35:14.400 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, I was a
classical dancer,

00:35:14.400 --> 00:35:18.740 align:middle line:10%
so I was supposed to give
my first performance.

00:35:18.740 --> 00:35:25.070 align:middle line:10%
So, in front of him, I used to
do the practice all the time.

00:35:25.070 --> 00:35:30.250 align:middle line:10%
So when he used to correct
me during these yoga postures

00:35:30.250 --> 00:35:32.410 align:middle line:10%
and all, he used to correct me.

00:35:32.410 --> 00:35:36.510 align:middle line:10%
But even when I
used to have a bath,

00:35:36.510 --> 00:35:38.390 align:middle line:10%
he used to come
after having a bath

00:35:38.390 --> 00:35:39.970 align:middle line:10%
and tell me that,
Savita, come on.

00:35:39.970 --> 00:35:40.790 align:middle line:10%
Do this.

00:35:40.790 --> 00:35:44.850 align:middle line:10%
So even during the bath,
he was thinking about my--

00:35:44.850 --> 00:35:49.060 align:middle line:10%
how I had to improve my
dance with their expressions,

00:35:49.060 --> 00:35:52.150 align:middle line:10%
with the gestures, with
the hand movements.

00:35:52.150 --> 00:35:54.230 align:middle line:10%
>> Hand movements,
palm movements.

00:35:54.230 --> 00:35:56.670 align:middle line:10%
He was graceful, actually.

00:35:56.670 --> 00:35:58.600 align:middle line:10%
He wanted to learn,
actually, dance.

00:35:58.600 --> 00:36:01.060 align:middle line:10%
>> He was thinking about
actually becoming a classical

00:36:01.060 --> 00:36:05.890 align:middle line:10%
dancer rather than practitioner
of yoga at some stage in life.

00:36:05.890 --> 00:36:11.620 align:middle line:10%
And that's why he once saw
Uday Shankar in a ballet.

00:36:11.620 --> 00:36:13.040 align:middle line:10%
And he was so fascinated.

00:36:13.040 --> 00:36:15.520 align:middle line:10%
Then he said, why
not find out the way

00:36:15.520 --> 00:36:17.920 align:middle line:10%
that I will teach him yoga,
and he will teach me dance.

00:36:17.920 --> 00:36:21.250 align:middle line:10%
>> But Uday Shankar was not
interested in yoga, it seems.

00:36:21.250 --> 00:36:23.190 align:middle line:10%
So he could not continue.

00:36:23.190 --> 00:36:25.750 align:middle line:10%
But music, he was
very much interested.

00:36:25.750 --> 00:36:28.630 align:middle line:10%
Both my parents were interested
in music to the point that

00:36:28.630 --> 00:36:33.520 align:middle line:10%
the interest was in
everybody's-- all the siblings.

00:36:33.520 --> 00:36:37.470 align:middle line:10%
And I used to play sitar for
my another sister Sunita.

00:36:37.470 --> 00:36:40.270 align:middle line:10%
Prashant and Vanita,
they used to play violin.

00:36:40.270 --> 00:36:41.920 align:middle line:10%
Savita danced.

00:36:41.920 --> 00:36:45.640 align:middle line:10%
Geeta learned vocal
music, then sitar, also.

00:36:45.640 --> 00:36:49.300 align:middle line:10%
So he used to teach us the
technique, how to play--

00:36:49.300 --> 00:36:53.230 align:middle line:10%
fingering work, wrist work,
and everything he used to tell.

00:36:53.230 --> 00:36:57.280 align:middle line:10%
And it used to make a lot of
difference in the technique.

00:36:57.280 --> 00:37:02.320 align:middle line:10%
>> Renowned and famous and
a great teacher as he was,

00:37:02.320 --> 00:37:04.280 align:middle line:10%
but when it came to
normal family life,

00:37:04.280 --> 00:37:07.470 align:middle line:10%
he was just like any ordinary
man-- like a very common man.

00:37:07.470 --> 00:37:10.030 align:middle line:10%
And that was very
endearing about him.

00:37:10.030 --> 00:37:13.630 align:middle line:10%
>> In the house, as a father,
he was very much lovable.

00:37:13.630 --> 00:37:15.800 align:middle line:10%
At the same time,
he was very strict.

00:37:15.800 --> 00:37:20.220 align:middle line:10%
>> He was not at all
strict whatsoever to me.

00:37:20.220 --> 00:37:24.010 align:middle line:10%
>> Actually, when his classes
were going on and while he used

00:37:24.010 --> 00:37:27.170 align:middle line:10%
to practice, it should
be pin drop silence.

00:37:27.170 --> 00:37:29.650 align:middle line:10%
We children never used
to make any noise.

00:37:29.650 --> 00:37:31.970 align:middle line:10%
He never used to like that.

00:37:31.970 --> 00:37:35.120 align:middle line:10%
But when and children were
playing, he used to practice.

00:37:35.120 --> 00:37:37.000 align:middle line:10%
They used to play cricket.

00:37:37.000 --> 00:37:40.090 align:middle line:10%
And he was also sometimes
laughing, playing with them.

00:37:40.090 --> 00:37:41.530 align:middle line:10%
>> Used to play with him a lot.

00:37:41.530 --> 00:37:42.700 align:middle line:10%
And he used to
practice as you go--

00:37:42.700 --> 00:37:44.283 align:middle line:10%
He would be practicing
in the hallway.

00:37:44.283 --> 00:37:46.230 align:middle line:10%
I used to go in the
hall, trouble him.

00:37:46.230 --> 00:37:48.230 align:middle line:10%
If he's sleeping, stand
on his legs or whatever.

00:37:48.230 --> 00:37:49.528 align:middle line:10%
Just play with him.

00:37:49.528 --> 00:37:51.070 align:middle line:10%
>> He had this thing
he used to say--

00:37:51.070 --> 00:37:52.750 align:middle line:10%
OK, I'll make you fly
like an aeroplane.

00:37:52.750 --> 00:37:57.280 align:middle line:10%
So he used to lay down on
his back and hold us like--

00:37:57.280 --> 00:37:58.950 align:middle line:10%
so we are kids, right?

00:37:58.950 --> 00:38:01.660 align:middle line:84%
So we are on-- so
his legs up, and we

00:38:01.660 --> 00:38:04.280 align:middle line:84%
are laying flat on his
legs and holding his hands.

00:38:04.280 --> 00:38:06.100 align:middle line:84%
And he is making us
fly like an aeroplane.

00:38:06.100 --> 00:38:08.710 align:middle line:84%
>> Sometimes in the morning,
when we would be sleeping late

00:38:08.710 --> 00:38:11.860 align:middle line:84%
and we would not wake up,
suddenly we would be woken up,

00:38:11.860 --> 00:38:15.020 align:middle line:84%
because he would be
walking on our legs.

00:38:15.020 --> 00:38:15.820 align:middle line:90%
So yes.

00:38:15.820 --> 00:38:18.310 align:middle line:84%
Then he would just laugh,
and he would walk off.

00:38:18.310 --> 00:38:19.720 align:middle line:90%
>> He was like a child--

00:38:19.720 --> 00:38:23.260 align:middle line:84%
full of life, full
of fun, his eyes

00:38:23.260 --> 00:38:26.020 align:middle line:84%
twinkling with mischief,
with that mischievous

00:38:26.020 --> 00:38:27.790 align:middle line:90%
smile on his face.

00:38:27.790 --> 00:38:29.700 align:middle line:90%
He was ready for an adventure.

00:38:29.700 --> 00:38:31.450 align:middle line:84%
So there are times
when we would have done

00:38:31.450 --> 00:38:32.790 align:middle line:90%
some crazy things with him.

00:38:32.790 --> 00:38:37.150 align:middle line:10%
And he would be ready for a game
of cricket, or sit on a swing,

00:38:37.150 --> 00:38:39.880 align:middle line:10%
or be ready to stand on
his head in Sirsasana

00:38:39.880 --> 00:38:41.290 align:middle line:10%
on the edge of a cliff--

00:38:41.290 --> 00:38:43.343 align:middle line:10%
challenge us to do
things which he did.

00:38:43.343 --> 00:38:45.010 align:middle line:84%
>> So if we were at
the top of the hill,

00:38:45.010 --> 00:38:48.100 align:middle line:84%
he used to like to go to
the edge and to sort of do

00:38:48.100 --> 00:38:49.030 align:middle line:90%
the adventurous thing.

00:38:49.030 --> 00:38:50.575 align:middle line:90%
And he used to take us along.

00:38:50.575 --> 00:38:52.200 align:middle line:84%
And our parents, my
father, was scared.

00:38:52.200 --> 00:38:53.033 align:middle line:90%
Hey, don't go there.

00:38:53.033 --> 00:38:54.555 align:middle line:90%
You'll fall down.

00:38:54.555 --> 00:38:57.640 align:middle line:84%
So I remember once, we had
been to the Nandi Hills.

00:38:57.640 --> 00:39:00.130 align:middle line:84%
And there is this
place called Tipu Drop.

00:39:00.130 --> 00:39:03.410 align:middle line:84%
So that's where Tipu Sultan, he
used to push down his enemies.

00:39:03.410 --> 00:39:07.440 align:middle line:84%
So there is like a very steep
fall and there is a wall.

00:39:07.440 --> 00:39:09.330 align:middle line:90%
And the wall doesn't even like--

00:39:09.330 --> 00:39:12.170 align:middle line:84%
the comparable kind of a wall,
it doesn't have a flat surface.

00:39:12.170 --> 00:39:14.920 align:middle line:84%
It was a curved
surface on top of it.

00:39:14.920 --> 00:39:16.900 align:middle line:90%
And so that does--

00:39:16.900 --> 00:39:18.550 align:middle line:90%
so he got up on the wall.

00:39:18.550 --> 00:39:20.800 align:middle line:84%
But there's a steep
fall on the other side.

00:39:20.800 --> 00:39:23.170 align:middle line:84%
He's wearing his
[INAUDIBLE] and was sort

00:39:23.170 --> 00:39:24.130 align:middle line:90%
of walking like a king.

00:39:24.130 --> 00:39:26.410 align:middle line:84%
And we are all scared,
because it's very windy

00:39:26.410 --> 00:39:29.000 align:middle line:84%
and the other side
is totally steep.

00:39:29.000 --> 00:39:29.800 align:middle line:90%
And he's laughing.

00:39:29.800 --> 00:39:31.258 align:middle line:84%
So he's enjoying
walking like that.

00:39:31.258 --> 00:39:32.758 align:middle line:84%
And he's calling
us-- you also come.

00:39:32.758 --> 00:39:33.670 align:middle line:90%
You also climb.

00:39:33.670 --> 00:39:36.670 align:middle line:84%
>> And we had once gone on a
family picnic to Mulshi during

00:39:36.670 --> 00:39:38.420 align:middle line:90%
the monsoon.

00:39:38.420 --> 00:39:40.313 align:middle line:84%
So Guruji stopped
the car and said--

00:39:40.313 --> 00:39:41.230 align:middle line:90%
he said, stop the car.

00:39:41.230 --> 00:39:42.860 align:middle line:90%
This will be our picnic spot.

00:39:42.860 --> 00:39:44.470 align:middle line:90%
So there was a mild waterfall.

00:39:44.470 --> 00:39:46.360 align:middle line:90%
There was some slippery rocks.

00:39:46.360 --> 00:39:48.600 align:middle line:10%
And we all just sat
there, opened up

00:39:48.600 --> 00:39:52.210 align:middle line:10%
what we'd got for eating, and
laughing, playing in the water.

00:39:52.210 --> 00:39:53.290 align:middle line:90%
And he called out to me.

00:39:53.290 --> 00:39:56.410 align:middle line:84%
And he said, hey,
do Sirsasana her.

00:39:56.410 --> 00:40:00.040 align:middle line:90%
And I was so terrified.

00:40:00.040 --> 00:40:01.510 align:middle line:90%
He said, do.

00:40:01.510 --> 00:40:03.790 align:middle line:84%
I said, I can not do,
because I can not balance.

00:40:03.790 --> 00:40:04.810 align:middle line:90%
He said, somebody will hold you.

00:40:04.810 --> 00:40:06.060 align:middle line:90%
So what if you can no balance?

00:40:06.060 --> 00:40:07.460 align:middle line:90%
Just do the pose.

00:40:07.460 --> 00:40:09.850 align:middle line:84%
And I am fighting with my
grandfather at that time,

00:40:09.850 --> 00:40:11.470 align:middle line:84%
trying to convince
my grandfather

00:40:11.470 --> 00:40:14.840 align:middle line:84%
that this granddaughter
can balance in Sirsasana.

00:40:14.840 --> 00:40:17.980 align:middle line:84%
And that's when the
teacher in him came out.

00:40:17.980 --> 00:40:20.930 align:middle line:84%
And he said, if you
don't do it now--

00:40:20.930 --> 00:40:22.550 align:middle line:90%
and he said, I will do it.

00:40:22.550 --> 00:40:26.810 align:middle line:84%
So I got doubly terrified that
it's so slippery, [INAUDIBLE]

00:40:26.810 --> 00:40:29.380 align:middle line:90%
and, you know, water.

00:40:29.380 --> 00:40:31.660 align:middle line:84%
But Guruji is
saying, I will do it.

00:40:31.660 --> 00:40:33.820 align:middle line:84%
If something happens,
what will my family think?

00:40:33.820 --> 00:40:35.900 align:middle line:84%
What will-- they'll
point fingers at me.

00:40:35.900 --> 00:40:39.510 align:middle line:84%
So the stress-- that stress
made me do Sirsasana.

00:40:39.510 --> 00:40:41.670 align:middle line:84%
And he taught me something
in that Sirsasana, also.

00:40:41.670 --> 00:40:43.720 align:middle line:84%
>> At home, this used
to happen very often,

00:40:43.720 --> 00:40:45.350 align:middle line:84%
where suddenly he'd say,
[INAUDIBLE] come here.

00:40:45.350 --> 00:40:46.150 align:middle line:90%
Do this.

00:40:46.150 --> 00:40:47.710 align:middle line:90%
Let me show you something.

00:40:47.710 --> 00:40:49.420 align:middle line:90%
And he's teaching us.

00:40:49.420 --> 00:40:50.480 align:middle line:90%
So if you're doing--

00:40:50.480 --> 00:40:52.720 align:middle line:84%
like say you're doing
Urdva Dhanurasana.

00:40:52.720 --> 00:40:54.625 align:middle line:90%
So you'll fall and you come up.

00:40:54.625 --> 00:40:57.470 align:middle line:84%
So he had this way of-- he
used to just hold us out

00:40:57.470 --> 00:40:59.480 align:middle line:84%
of the tip of the
[INAUDIBLE] there.

00:40:59.480 --> 00:41:02.970 align:middle line:84%
And then, when we had to come
up, he'd just do a small tug,

00:41:02.970 --> 00:41:04.743 align:middle line:84%
and we were able to
come up very fast.

00:41:04.743 --> 00:41:06.410 align:middle line:84%
It's almost like he
would just say, see,

00:41:06.410 --> 00:41:07.463 align:middle line:90%
I have magic in my hand.

00:41:07.463 --> 00:41:09.130 align:middle line:84%
I just pull, and
you're able to come up.

00:41:09.130 --> 00:41:11.080 align:middle line:84%
>> Even in the family
lunch occasion,

00:41:11.080 --> 00:41:14.290 align:middle line:84%
sometimes after lunch he would
say, hey, come do Sirsasana.

00:41:14.290 --> 00:41:15.880 align:middle line:84%
And I would tell
him, no, grandfather.

00:41:15.880 --> 00:41:16.510 align:middle line:90%
I just ate.

00:41:16.510 --> 00:41:17.520 align:middle line:84%
And he said,
nothing will happen.

00:41:17.520 --> 00:41:18.320 align:middle line:90%
Do.

00:41:18.320 --> 00:41:24.520 align:middle line:84%
So that kind of yoga
anytime, laughter anytime,

00:41:24.520 --> 00:41:25.600 align:middle line:90%
teasing me anytime.

00:41:25.600 --> 00:41:27.430 align:middle line:90%
So that always was on.

00:41:27.430 --> 00:41:31.377 align:middle line:10%
>> He used to be always
excited like a child when his

00:41:31.377 --> 00:41:33.460 align:middle line:10%
grandchildren and great
grandchildren were around,

00:41:33.460 --> 00:41:34.842 align:middle line:10%
especially.

00:41:34.842 --> 00:41:36.550 align:middle line:10%
>> I couldn't resist
taking Guruji's car.

00:41:36.550 --> 00:41:38.140 align:middle line:10%
It was an Ambassador
at that point in time.

00:41:38.140 --> 00:41:39.563 align:middle line:10%
And I'd take it
out, and he used--

00:41:39.563 --> 00:41:41.200 align:middle line:10%
I used to ask him,
Tata, are you coming?

00:41:41.200 --> 00:41:42.460 align:middle line:10%
And he would not bat an eyelid.

00:41:42.460 --> 00:41:43.627 align:middle line:10%
He would say, yes, let's go.

00:41:43.627 --> 00:41:44.740 align:middle line:10%
Let's have fun.

00:41:44.740 --> 00:41:45.690 align:middle line:10%
The man loved life.

00:41:45.690 --> 00:41:46.780 align:middle line:10%
He was full of life.

00:41:46.780 --> 00:41:48.490 align:middle line:10%
And that time, I didn't realize.

00:41:48.490 --> 00:41:49.690 align:middle line:10%
I used to just take him.

