Glasgow is growing all the time.

01:01:34.860 --> 01:01:37.090 align:middle line:84%
So we now have
some new teachers.

01:01:37.090 --> 01:01:40.310 align:middle line:84%
We now have a far
bigger pool of people

01:01:40.310 --> 01:01:41.852 align:middle line:84%
