01:01:45.530 --> 01:01:48.800 align:middle line:84%
in that way when she started
practicing as a young boy.

01:01:48.800 --> 01:01:50.660 align:middle line:10%
>> But when you
practice Iyengar Yoga,

01:01:50.660 --> 01:01:54.250 align:middle line:10%
