01:01:57.820 --> 01:02:01.480 align:middle line:84%
And you meet people who
share the same values

01:02:01.480 --> 01:02:03.450 align:middle line:90%
and have the same views.

01:02:03.450 --> 01:02:07.340 align:middle line:84%
>> I feel Guruji's art has
brought people together,

01:02:07.340 --> 01:02:10.790 align:middle line:84%
not only in Birmingham,
but all over the world.

01:02:10.790 --> 01:02:15.640 align:middle line:10%
>> And sometimes Guruji calls
us my children in the field

01:02:15.640 --> 01:02:17.320 align:middle line:10%
of yoga.

01:02:17.320 --> 01:02:22.510 align:middle line:10%
So I know I have beautiful
sisters and brothers

01:02:22.510 --> 01:02:24.190 align:middle line:10%
all around the world.

01:02:24.190 --> 01:02:29.666 align:middle line:10%
>> Everyone is like a branch and
flower and leaves from all over

01:02:29.666 --> 01:02:37.330 align:middle line:10%
the world to spread Iyengar Yoga
knowledge all over the world.

01:02:37.330 --> 01:02:42.210 align:middle line:84%
>> And another joy has been
to be part of that community,

01:02:42.210 --> 01:02:45.220 align:middle line:84%
to be part of these
like minded people--

01:02:45.220 --> 01:02:47.580 align:middle line:90%
what we share in common.

01:02:47.580 --> 01:02:51.510 align:middle line:84%
And the complete sense
of devastation and loss

01:02:51.510 --> 01:02:56.460 align:middle line:84%
that community felt when Mr.
Iyengar died, when Guruji died,

01:02:56.460 --> 01:03:00.130 align:middle line:90%
was just so overwhelming.

01:03:00.130 --> 01:03:06.680 align:middle line:84%
It was almost curious that
somebody who lived so far away

01:03:06.680 --> 01:03:08.510 align:middle line:84%
could have that
influence in people.

01:03:08.510 --> 01:03:12.040 align:middle line:84%
And everyone felt
entirely bereft.

01:03:12.040 --> 01:03:15.380 align:middle line:10%
>> He has helped
millions of people,

01:03:15.380 --> 01:03:18.020 align:middle line:10%
and people who have
different lives.

01:03:18.020 --> 01:03:20.900 align:middle line:10%
>> He was open to expand
and pass his knowledge

01:03:20.900 --> 01:03:21.740 align:middle line:10%
to everybody.

01:03:21.740 --> 01:03:24.805 align:middle line:10%
He didn't make difference
at all who you were.

01:03:24.805 --> 01:03:26.230 align:middle line:90%
>> He love everybody.

01:03:26.230 --> 01:03:31.660 align:middle line:84%
He never had any
discrimination about anybody's

01:03:31.660 --> 01:03:34.730 align:middle line:84%
social background,
economic background.

01:03:34.730 --> 01:03:39.410 align:middle line:10%
>> And then he said, I
welcome every student of yoga.

01:03:39.410 --> 01:03:42.320 align:middle line:84%
And I feel that
every person needs

01:03:42.320 --> 01:03:44.390 align:middle line:90%
to make a beginning somewhere.

01:03:44.390 --> 01:03:49.100 align:middle line:10%
>> Guruji's yoga has
taught me how to be--

01:03:49.100 --> 01:03:53.220 align:middle line:10%
how to sit, how just
stand, how to walk,

01:03:53.220 --> 01:04:00.740 align:middle line:10%
how to run, how to eat, how
to sleep, how to observe,

01:04:00.740 --> 01:04:02.330 align:middle line:10%
and how to absorb.

01:04:02.330 --> 01:04:06.020 align:middle line:10%
>> It satisfies me creatively--
the joy of exploring,

01:04:06.020 --> 01:04:09.240 align:middle line:10%
and learning new things,
and trying new things.

01:04:09.240 --> 01:04:11.510 align:middle line:10%
>> And the reason I can
continue to be a photographer,

01:04:11.510 --> 01:04:14.980 align:middle line:10%
carry those heavy backpacks,
and movement is because I do

01:04:14.980 --> 01:04:15.910 align:middle line:10%
Iyengar Yoga.

01:04:15.910 --> 01:04:27.530 align:middle line:10%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

01:04:27.530 --> 01:04:31.940 align:middle line:10%
>> It was due to Guruji
that I was able to walk.

01:04:31.940 --> 01:04:33.530 align:middle line:84%
It was to due to
Guruji that I was

01:04:33.530 --> 01:04:39.930 align:middle line:84%
able to put off having back
surgery for over 40 years.

01:04:39.930 --> 01:04:42.220 align:middle line:10%
>> I'm a different person.

01:04:42.220 --> 01:04:44.180 align:middle line:10%
I got new legs.

01:04:44.180 --> 01:04:46.040 align:middle line:10%
I got new spine.

01:04:46.040 --> 01:04:51.200 align:middle line:10%
>> Through doing this forward
bending, headband wrapping,

01:04:51.200 --> 01:04:55.490 align:middle line:10%
slow Iyengar Yoga
rehabilitation process,

01:04:55.490 --> 01:04:58.250 align:middle line:10%
we've managed to bring these
headaches under control within

01:04:58.250 --> 01:05:03.420 align:middle line:10%
the first two months of
my two brain surgeries.

01:05:03.420 --> 01:05:07.290 align:middle line:10%
>> Today, Iyengar Yoga has
become indispensable for me.

01:05:07.290 --> 01:05:12.920 align:middle line:10%
With my medical limitations, I
have learned to live happily.

01:05:12.920 --> 01:05:16.010 align:middle line:84%
>> This was a type of yoga
that I would be able to do

01:05:16.010 --> 01:05:17.710 align:middle line:90%
into my golden years.

01:05:17.710 --> 01:05:20.510 align:middle line:84%
And since my golden years
are right around the corner,

01:05:20.510 --> 01:05:23.750 align:middle line:84%
and here I am, still
doing Iyengar Yoga.

01:05:23.750 --> 01:05:27.590 align:middle line:10%
>> At the ripe age of 60,
I am doing Sirsasana and--

01:05:27.590 --> 01:05:30.530 align:middle line:10%
I don't know-- six minutes
every day for a long time.

01:05:30.530 --> 01:05:36.290 align:middle line:10%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

01:05:36.290 --> 01:05:41.300 align:middle line:10%
>> And if I stick to what he has
taught and what he's developed,

01:05:41.300 --> 01:05:42.980 align:middle line:10%
I will find my way.

01:05:42.980 --> 01:05:46.100 align:middle line:84%
>> So whatever I am today,
or whatever I am doing,

01:05:46.100 --> 01:05:48.430 align:middle line:84%
it's only and only
because of Guruji.

01:05:48.430 --> 01:05:53.570 align:middle line:84%
So about his legacy, is what
one is that is his legacy.

01:05:53.570 --> 01:05:56.340 align:middle line:84%
What he has made us,
that is his legacy.

01:05:56.340 --> 01:05:58.600 align:middle line:84%
And that is what we
are carrying with us.

01:05:58.600 --> 01:06:03.110 align:middle line:84%
>> And he said, as long
as mine students can give

01:06:03.110 --> 01:06:07.220 align:middle line:84%
their students a taste of the
sensitivity alertness that

01:06:07.220 --> 01:06:08.990 align:middle line:90%
I'm giving you all--

01:06:08.990 --> 01:06:12.320 align:middle line:84%
as long as that's there,
this will live on.

01:06:12.320 --> 01:06:14.345 align:middle line:10%
>> 29 years later,
I'm grandmother,

01:06:14.345 --> 01:06:17.750 align:middle line:10%
and I'm still practicing and
learning from the teachings

01:06:17.750 --> 01:06:19.850 align:middle line:10%
of this extraordinary man.

01:06:19.850 --> 01:06:23.780 align:middle line:84%
His legacy lives on through
the generations of my family.

01:06:23.780 --> 01:06:37.490 align:middle line:10%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

01:06:37.490 --> 01:06:41.560 align:middle line:10%
>> So he has left behind us a
boon for humanity with all his

01:06:41.560 --> 01:06:46.850 align:middle line:10%
research and application in the
field of yoga to heal the human

01:06:46.850 --> 01:06:48.220 align:middle line:10%
body and mind.

01:06:48.220 --> 01:06:51.140 align:middle line:10%
So I think it is up
to us to use it now.

01:06:51.140 --> 01:06:54.110 align:middle line:84%
>> We also have the
responsibility to keep

01:06:54.110 --> 01:06:57.650 align:middle line:84%
on spreading his teaching
and the values he wanted

01:06:57.650 --> 01:06:58.640 align:middle line:90%
to promote.

01:06:58.640 --> 01:07:02.800 align:middle line:84%
>> And to help other people to
understand how important it is

01:07:02.800 --> 01:07:08.270 align:middle line:84%
to make the proper asanas with
guidance, with understanding,

01:07:08.270 --> 01:07:09.680 align:middle line:90%
with alignment.

01:07:09.680 --> 01:07:14.990 align:middle line:10%
>> His fantastic success lies
now for us as a foundation

01:07:14.990 --> 01:07:17.040 align:middle line:10%
to build upon further.

01:07:17.040 --> 01:07:21.240 align:middle line:10%
>> So we must pass on to
the next generation for them

01:07:21.240 --> 01:07:23.790 align:middle line:10%
to continue Guruji's legacy.

01:07:23.790 --> 01:07:26.300 align:middle line:84%
>> And that's why we
continue to teach.

01:07:26.300 --> 01:07:27.770 align:middle line:90%
That's why we want to give.

01:07:27.770 --> 01:07:32.690 align:middle line:84%
We want to help people the way
he helped, the way he taught.

01:07:32.690 --> 01:07:34.880 align:middle line:84%
>> Because this is what
we're supposed to do--

01:07:34.880 --> 01:07:38.770 align:middle line:90%
to continue, to let go, show.

01:07:38.770 --> 01:07:41.720 align:middle line:84%
Plant the seed so
that everybody can

01:07:41.720 --> 01:07:44.960 align:middle line:90%
see that Guruji is not dead.

01:07:44.960 --> 01:07:47.000 align:middle line:90%
Guruji is only, as he said--

01:07:47.000 --> 01:07:49.650 align:middle line:84%
I'm only going to
change my clothes.

01:07:49.650 --> 01:07:51.960 align:middle line:90%
I am not going anywhere.

01:07:51.960 --> 01:07:54.910 align:middle line:84%
I'm only going to
change my clothes.

01:07:54.910 --> 01:08:00.050 align:middle line:84%
>> Every aspect of my
life is linked with him--

01:08:00.050 --> 01:08:05.540 align:middle line:84%
whether I sleep, whether I
eat, whether I practice yoga.

01:08:05.540 --> 01:08:07.760 align:middle line:90%
Everywhere, Guruji is with me.

01:08:07.760 --> 01:08:09.950 align:middle line:90%
>> So I am lucky.

01:08:09.950 --> 01:08:13.370 align:middle line:84%
I was very lucky to have
been in and around him--

01:08:13.370 --> 01:08:16.970 align:middle line:84%
not just in the institute during
the classes or during practice,

01:08:16.970 --> 01:08:22.250 align:middle line:84%
but also at home, because each--
now that he's no longer there,

01:08:22.250 --> 01:08:32.410 align:middle line:84%
each memory that I have of him
is a valuable thing for me now.

01:08:32.410 --> 01:08:33.830 align:middle line:90%
>> Guruji is never far from us.

01:08:33.830 --> 01:08:35.779 align:middle line:84%
He's certainly
never far from me.

01:08:35.779 --> 01:08:38.210 align:middle line:90%
He's always there on my mat.

01:08:38.210 --> 01:08:42.649 align:middle line:84%
And those lessons and
the tools that he gave

01:08:42.649 --> 01:08:43.850 align:middle line:90%
continue to evolve.

01:08:43.850 --> 01:08:46.520 align:middle line:84%
And for that, I'm
eternally grateful.

01:08:46.520 --> 01:08:51.200 align:middle line:10%
>> And he really tuned in and
made us understand that his

01:08:51.200 --> 01:08:53.660 align:middle line:10%
method wasn't his method--

01:08:53.660 --> 01:08:56.300 align:middle line:10%
that he was teaching
yoga, and that we

01:08:56.300 --> 01:08:58.430 align:middle line:10%
were calling it Iyengar Yoga.

01:08:58.430 --> 01:09:01.130 align:middle line:84%
And that it was something
greater than him.

01:09:01.130 --> 01:09:03.260 align:middle line:84%
And then what he taught
us is something so much

01:09:03.260 --> 01:09:05.029 align:middle line:90%
greater than all of us.

01:09:05.029 --> 01:09:12.529 align:middle line:10%
>> We can practice,
and go on in our life,

01:09:12.529 --> 01:09:19.800 align:middle line:10%
and follow the path so that
maybe one day his sentence,

01:09:19.800 --> 01:09:25.520 align:middle line:10%
may my end be your
beginning, may be true.

01:09:25.520 --> 01:09:29.000 align:middle line:84%
>> I always thought of
Guruji's teaching as rainfall.

01:09:29.000 --> 01:09:32.330 align:middle line:84%
It was a downpour, and
whoever was lucky enough

01:09:32.330 --> 01:09:34.850 align:middle line:84%
to be in that field,
received that.

01:09:34.850 --> 01:09:39.180 align:middle line:84%
So he never chose,
or he never selected,

01:09:39.180 --> 01:09:43.050 align:middle line:84%
that he would teach this
person and not that person.

01:09:43.050 --> 01:09:45.810 align:middle line:84%
So whoever was there
just received it.

01:09:45.810 --> 01:09:47.270 align:middle line:90%
So it is the--

01:09:47.270 --> 01:09:49.250 align:middle line:84%
the onus is upon
each one of us who

01:09:49.250 --> 01:09:53.060 align:middle line:84%
was received that
rainfall to keep it alive

01:09:53.060 --> 01:09:55.410 align:middle line:84%
and to pass it on
as [INAUDIBLE]..

01:09:55.410 --> 01:09:59.670 align:middle line:10%
>> If you are practicing
yoga, do not get carried away,

01:09:59.670 --> 01:10:00.948 align:middle line:10%
but continue.

01:10:00.948 --> 01:10:03.320 align:middle line:10%
The light will come on its own.

01:10:03.320 --> 01:10:05.950 align:middle line:10%
The fruit will fall to the
ground when it is ripe.

01:10:05.950 --> 01:10:07.290 align:middle line:10%
Is it not?

01:10:07.290 --> 01:10:09.160 align:middle line:10%
We are practicing yoga.

01:10:09.160 --> 01:10:11.120 align:middle line:10%
So as we practicing,
the fruit has

01:10:11.120 --> 01:10:15.910 align:middle line:10%
to come when the body and the
mind is right for it to fall.

01:10:15.910 --> 01:10:19.410 align:middle line:10%
Then that is known
as self-realisation.

01:10:19.410 --> 01:10:21.090 align:middle line:10%
Because you have to
tend to the tree.

01:10:21.090 --> 01:10:23.340 align:middle line:10%
You have to look up to the
tree for the fruit to come.

01:10:23.340 --> 01:10:26.223 align:middle line:10%
So also, you have to look after
the body and the mind, which

01:10:26.223 --> 01:10:29.580 align:middle line:10%
are the tree of the soul, which
are the branches of the soul.

01:10:29.580 --> 01:10:31.305 align:middle line:10%
So they have to
be looked after so

01:10:31.305 --> 01:10:33.480 align:middle line:10%
that the essence
may come out and you

01:10:33.480 --> 01:10:35.180 align:middle line:10%
drink the essence of the soul.

